ector since the 													Internet.																										more (http://canadasmallcap-info.com/080E10000711171532171F5C11130E40404147440E4046434145410E400E434746424342410E08.aspx)																										&nbsp;																																					&nbsp;																																																																														Newfound Liquidity Will Send 													Gold to $1000 (http://canadasmallcap-info.com/080E10000711171532171F5C11130E40404147440E4046434145410E400E434746424340440E08.aspx)																										Brien Lundin, 													Gold Newsletter													According to Brien 													Lundin, we are &quot;entering a 													period of monetary 													accommodation&quot; which will 													likely send gold prices to 													$1000 by the end of 2008. 													Mr. Lundin believes that all 													metals should benefit from 													gold's appreciation, and 													silver, which has been 													laggard, may see the largest 													increase of the group. 													Listen to hear two 													Exploration companies, 													priced under $4, which were 													strong recommendations from 													Mr. Lundin.																																																				more (http://canadasmallcap-info.com/080E10000711171532171F5C11130E40404147440E4046434145410E400E434746424340440E08.aspx)													&nbsp;																																																																										REMOVE MY NAME																																																		&nbsp;																																																																			StockNewsCast.com feature stock reports are 								intended to be stock ideas, NOT recommendations. 								Please do your own research before investing. It 								is crucial that you at least look at current SEC 								filings and read the latest&nbsp;press releases. For 								continuing coverage of our highlighted stocks 								please sign up for our free newsletter. 	